                           text; abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs and text dividers;
                           elements of Ethiopic numerals; some other words, e.g., wa-kāʿǝba (e.g.,
                           fols. 110rb, 125rb), ṣällǝyu (e.g., fol. 31vb), halle luya (e.g., fols.
                           2vab, 3rab, 4vb, 25ra), wa-ʾǝmzǝ (e.,g., fols. 35rb, 41ra), wa-yǝbälu
